@startuml
participant "GitHub" as GH
participant "API Service" as API
participant "EventBridge" as EB
participant "Orchestrator Service" as OS
participant "DynamoDB" as DDB
participant "Analyse Service" as AS
participant "S3" as S3
participant "BigQuery" as BQ
participant "Publish Service" as PS

GH -> API: Webhook event
API -> API: Validate webhook
API -> EB: Enqueue event
EB -> OS: Trigger event processing
OS -> DDB: Fetch project configuration
OS -> DDB: Update event store
OS -> EB: Trigger analysis event
EB -> AS: Process analysis event
AS -> S3: Fetch raw coverage data
AS -> BQ: Query historical data
AS -> AS: Analyze coverage
AS -> DDB: Store analysis results
AS -> EB: Trigger publish event
EB -> PS: Process publish event
PS -> GH: Update PR with coverage report
PS -> DDB: Update event store
@enduml